    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "Revenue grew 6.0% year‑over‑year, driven primarily by Marketplace and Essentials.",
      "section_path": "1.1 Commentary"
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "Gross margin improved by 80 bps as inbound freight rates remained favorable and private label penetration increased.",
      "section_path": "1.1 Commentary"
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "Opex grew faster than sales due to higher store labor hours and incremental marketing spend, resulting in a slight decline in EBITDA margin.",
      "section_path": "1.1 Commentary"
    },
    {
