      "section_path": "3.1 Commentary"
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "Traffic increased 8.3%, but conversion rate declined slightly due to heavier assortment in early‑season apparel and ongoing experimentation on the homepage.",
      "section_path": "3.1 Commentary"
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "page": null,
      "type": "ListItem",
      "text": "Same‑day orders continue to grow as a share of digital volume, which is positive for customer satisfaction but puts pressure on fulfillment cost.",
